{"title":"2025 MADE Bike Show Returns August 22-24th and Tickets Are On Sale","link":"https://theradavist.com/2025-made-bike-show-returns/","date":1738760092000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/2025_Made_Bike_Show.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/2025_Made_Bike_Show.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/2025_Made_Bike_Show.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/2025_Made_Bike_Show.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/made-bike-show/\" target=\"_blank\">Made Bike Show</a> has announced its 2025 dates and ticket sales. The show will occur August 22-24 at Zidell Yards in Portland, OR. Exhibitor registration is open, and <a href=\"https://made.bike/event/the-made-handmade-bike-show-2025/\" target=\"_blank\">tickets</a> for 2025 MADE are now available…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Sour-Bikes-Crumble-Hardtail-19.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Sour-Bikes-Crumble-Hardtail-19.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Sour-Bikes-Crumble-Hardtail-19.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Sour-Bikes-Crumble-Hardtail-19.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Wolf-Tooth-Components-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Wolf-Tooth-Components-10.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Wolf-Tooth-Components-10.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Wolf-Tooth-Components-10.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-People-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-People-26.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-People-26.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-People-26.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Entering its third year, MADE continues its mission to elevate and inspire the craft by bringing <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/framebuilders/\" target=\"_blank\">framebuilders</a>, media, and makers together. The 2025 show will feature an expanded floor plan, allowing more builders and brands to participate with a captive audience of consumers and media.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Prova-Cycles-Ti-Full-Suspension-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Prova-Cycles-Ti-Full-Suspension-4.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Prova-Cycles-Ti-Full-Suspension-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Prova-Cycles-Ti-Full-Suspension-4.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rare-Earth-Rascal-Saint-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rare-Earth-Rascal-Saint-13.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rare-Earth-Rascal-Saint-13.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rare-Earth-Rascal-Saint-13.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bantam-Belt-Drive-Single-Speed-Commuter-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bantam-Belt-Drive-Single-Speed-Commuter-3.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bantam-Belt-Drive-Single-Speed-Commuter-3.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bantam-Belt-Drive-Single-Speed-Commuter-3.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The show’s expansion will remove the existing waitlist for exhibitors, allowing everyone to attend and enjoy the experience.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show19.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show19.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show19.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show19.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show14.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show14.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show14.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Head_Shots_Head_Tubes_2024_MADE_Bike_Show2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>What to Expect at 2025 MADE:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>3 days of consumer, media, and industry activations</li>\n<li>Evening events and activations</li>\n<li>200+ Builders and Brands</li>\n<li>New larger floorplan</li>\n<li>Subsidized Booth Space for New Builders</li>\n<li>Evening Events and Activations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Get your tickets at <a href=\"https://made.bike/event/the-made-handmade-bike-show-2025/\" target=\"_blank\">MADE</a>.</p>\n<p>The Radavist will return to 2025 MADE for more of our industry-leading Reportage. See you there!</p>\n<p>Check out last year’s MADE Coverage in our Related Archives below.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2025-made-bike-show-returns/\">2025 MADE Bike Show Returns August 22-24th and Tickets Are On Sale</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"20ad4c2ed82d74eeecdd0559034b6a494a3ba8ca1389d45184946e220e52d1b8","category":"Cycling"}